      <h3>Mike Perkins</h3>
       <img src="/assets/pics/members/mike-perkins.jpg" />
      
      <p>Mike tries to bring original and funny stories. He cannot resist a good pun, and loves to end his stories with a punch, or a curveball.</p>

<p>He is also a lover of the mendip hills, coming here often even as a child.</p>

    </div>
