    <div class="member">
      <h3>Peter Janes</h3>
       <img src="/assets/pics/members/peter-janes.jpg" />
      
      <p>A ballad singer, and lover of the morose. In many of the ballads he chooses to bring, the protagonist dies a gory, yet matter of fact death.</p>

<p>Peter loves the ballads for the self contained sense of history they carry.</p>

